N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 124.4 - List of officers and employees

State Regulations
A list setting forth the name, public
office address, title and salary of every officer or employee of the Office of

Court Administration shall be available for public inspection and copying at
the business office of the records access officer. Notes
